{"tid":500142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"核電站組件出廠時焊接縫遠超標, 離香港約130km","createTime":"2017-12-15T13:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T01:43:29.000Z","uid":69930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"86e4fc2ca6a56dce7ddb2f59f2a7ecf753407c18","tid":500142,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">距離香港約130公里<br />\n除氧器出問題或影響堆芯降溫 <br />\n文件揭台山核電站組件出廠時焊接縫遠超標</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/213058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F213058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82c389d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n (傳真社香港14日電) - 中國廣核電力股份有限公司(中廣核，1816)周二回應FactWire傳真社調查報道，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">承認台山核電站1號機組的除氧器存在「局部缺陷」</span></strong>，正採取更換措施，又指除氧器不屬核安全相關系統。但有刊登在國家學術期刊的技術研究報告指出，該<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">除氧器2012年出廠時已存在缺陷，導致焊合前需要現場加工「矯型」。過往曾有核電站因除氧器內部水位波動，影響反應堆芯降溫能力，包括距離最近香港的大亞灣核電站及嶺澳核電站。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/213105_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F213105_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5e4fa014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/single-post/2017/12/14/除氧器出問題或影響堆芯降溫-文件揭台山核電站組件出廠時焊接縫遠超標\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fsingle-post%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F%E9%99%A4%E6%B0%A7%E5%99%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%88%96%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%A0%86%E8%8A%AF%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%AB-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%8F%AD%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%B1%E6%A0%B8%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%99%E7%B5%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%87%BA%E5%BB%A0%E6%99%82%E7%84%8A%E6%8E%A5%E7%B8%AB%E9%81%A0%E8%B6%85%E6%A8%99&d=2rNSGEhzOSfKEq7qg3fthI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4feee558\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/single-post/2017/12/14/除氧器出問題或影響堆芯降溫-文件揭台山核電站組件出廠時焊接縫遠超標</a>"},{"pid":"44022b2e6b3416587fc3a536fb41235b35d800dc","tid":500142,"uid":70786,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:45:02.000Z","msg":"現場加工「矯型」都得咁condom都得啦"},{"pid":"b44ab41f886c7328f83476faa228ed0d62523b53","tid":500142,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"樓價跌福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a2cbe0b6f36fcd8f8b3f71d2488e116af54084","tid":500142,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T13:47:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<br />\n日日送大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3f71083ab09fc5bbe89cbfa9d61c9f0bbd5b44","tid":500142,"uid":69930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現場加工「矯型」都得咁condom都得啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ce6d6fadd6ad2920397efaf6615394f3a96370","tid":500142,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"真係好撚野"},{"pid":"37813d8e24afc1d1e990fb42384960b9c5610a15","tid":500142,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"恭喜曬"},{"pid":"187f36d75c3ecbeae7128f0d3b0fc8c42bea7ed4","tid":500142,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">距離香港約130公里<br />\n除氧器出問題或影響堆芯降溫 <br />\n文件揭台山核電站組件出廠時焊接縫遠超標</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/213058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F213058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82c389d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br 